  
\title{ThCocompleteCategory}
\tag{theory}

 \p{Theory of a *(finitely) cocomplete category*}\p{Finite colimits are presented in biased style, via finite coproducts and coequalizers. The axioms are dual to those of [\code{ThCompleteCategory}](@ref).}
